    "title": "SeaKing H10 White Fiberglass Fillet Table (L32.7\" x W15.7\")",
    "body_html": "<p data-end=\"144\" data-start=\"96\"><strong data-end=\"144\" data-start=\"96\">SeaKing SK-H10 Premium Fiberglass Filet Board [white]</strong></p>\n<p data-end=\"387\" data-start=\"146\">Handcrafted from full composite materials of the highest quality, the <strong data-end=\"234\" data-start=\"216\">SeaKing SK-H10</strong> is built to perform and endure. Featuring a <strong data-end=\"320\" data-start=\"279\">UV-resistant PE plastic cutting board</strong>, this model combines durability with a sleek, functional design.</p>\n<p data-end=\"754\" data-start=\"389\">Designed for serious anglers, the SK-H10 includes <strong data-end=\"476\" data-start=\"439\">a large integrated sink and drain</strong>, with <strong data-end=\"523\" data-start=\"483\">optional rod holders and cup holders</strong> for added versatility. A <strong data-end=\"577\" data-start=\"549\">spacious rear knife tray</strong> keeps tools within easy reach, while the <strong data-end=\"639\" data-start=\"619\">ergonomic layout</strong> maximizes usable cutting area without taking up valuable deck space, making it the ideal addition for any boat.</p>",
